      * PGM INTERFACE PARAMETER
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
      *@출력영역 확보를 위한 INTERFACE정의
       01  XZUGOTMY-CA.
           COPY  XZUGOTMY.

       01  XIJICOMM-CA.
           COPY  XIJICOMM.
      *   Sub-Limit현황(미기표포함)조회
       01  XDJL4821-CA.
           COPY  XDJL4821.

